    <item>
      <title>通用汽车与联邦贸易委员会就共享驾驶员数据达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/general-motors-settles-with-ftc-over-sharing-private-driver-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国联邦贸易委员会已与通用汽车公司达成和解，就该汽车制造商通过收集驾驶员个人数据并与第三方共享来欺骗驾驶员的指控达成和解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/general-motors-settles-with-ftc-over-sharing-private-driver-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 21:10:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普计划将加密货币指定为国家优先事项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-plans-to-designate-cryptocurrency-as-a-national-priority</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普计划发布一项行政命令，将加密货币提升为政策优先事项，并让业内人士在其政府内拥有发言权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/trump-plans-to-designate-cryptocurrency-as-a-national-priority</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 20:57:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国联邦贸易委员会 (FTC) 接近就《原神》中的“战利品箱”达成和解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ftc-nears-settlement-over-loot-boxes-in-popular-video-game</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，美国联邦贸易委员会正准备与热门视频游戏《原神》的开发商达成和解，原因是担心该游戏的赚钱机制具有欺骗性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/ftc-nears-settlement-over-loot-boxes-in-popular-video-game</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 19:02:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>FBI 警告特工，其认为去年电话记录遭到黑客攻击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/fbi-has-warned-agents-it-believes-hackers-stole-their-call-logs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博新闻社看到的一份文件显示，美国联邦调查局领导层警告称，他们认为去年侵入美国电话电报公司 (AT&amp;T Inc.) 系统的黑客窃取了其特工数月的通话和短信记录，这引发了局内一场保护机密线人身份的竞赛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/fbi-has-warned-agents-it-believes-hackers-stole-their-call-logs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 18:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Switch 2 预览版发布后，任天堂股价下跌，但未带来多少惊喜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/nintendo-to-unveil-next-generation-switch-2-in-april</link>
      <description><![CDATA[任天堂在一段两分钟的视频中展示了其下一代 Switch 2，并表示将于 4 月 2 日公布更多细节后，股价出现三个多月来的最大跌幅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-16/nintendo-to-unveil-next-generation-switch-2-in-april</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 16 Jan 2025 13:16:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
